multi_vehicle_communication.sh:接收/xtdrone/iris/id/cmd(flu、enu)    pose、vel、accel、cmd
                               发布  iris/id/mavros/setpoint_raw/local   target_motion

get_local_pose	               发布iris/id/mavros/vision_pose/pose



leader-follower键盘发出的速度指令为 /xtdrone/leader/cmd_vel_flu
非leader-follower键盘发出的指令为/xtdrone/iris/id/cmd_vel_flu



/iris_0/mavros/local_position/pose是准确真值
/xtdrone/iris_0/cmd_vel_flu是速度真值


cd ~/PX4_Firmware
roslaunch px4 indoor3.launch


cd ~/XTDrone/control/keyboard
python multirotor_keyboard_control.py iris 3 vel

cd ~/XTDrone/sensing/pose_ground_truth
python get_local_pose.py iris 3

./communication.sh
./stop_communication.sh


